  <h2>Let's Connect!</h2>
  <p>
    Let's Connect! Thanks for learning about me. I love connecting with fellow
    developers and tech enthusiasts. Feel free to reach out with questions, to
    discuss tech, or to share your journey. You can find me on <a
      href="https://www.github.com/sameer-ahmed123">Github</a
    >
  </p>
